<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>MindSpark — The Future Needs Better Thinkers</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;0,700;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --ink:#04040a;
  --paper:#f4efe6;
  --paper2:#ede7db;
  --gold:#c9922a;
  --gold2:#e8b84b;
  --gold-light:#f5d78e;
  --dim:#8a7f72;
  --border:rgba(201,146,42,0.2);
  --r:2px;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;font-size:16px}
body{
  font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;
  background:var(--ink);
  color:var(--paper);
  overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* ── SCROLLBAR ── */
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px}
::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--ink)}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--gold);border-radius:2px}

/* ── CANVAS ── */
#cosmos{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;pointer-events:none;opacity:0.5}

/* ── NAV ── */
nav{
  position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
  padding:0 6%;height:64px;
  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  background:rgba(4,4,10,0.8);
  backdrop-filter:blur(20px);
}
.logo{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
  font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.04em;
  color:var(--paper);cursor:pointer;
}
.logo span{color:var(--gold2)}
.nav-r{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:2rem}
.nav-r a{
  font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:rgba(244,239,230,0.45);text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.2s;
}
.nav-r a:hover{color:var(--paper)}
.nav-cta{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.78rem;font-weight:500;
  letter-spacing:0.04em;color:var(--gold2) !important;
  border:1px solid rgba(232,184,75,0.4);
  padding:8px 20px;border-radius:1px;
  transition:background 0.2s !important;
}
.nav-cta:hover{background:rgba(232,184,75,0.08) !important}

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero{
  min-height:100vh;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column;
  align-items:flex-start;justify-content:center;
  padding:0 6%;padding-top:64px;
  position:relative;z-index:1;
}
.hero-overline{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:500;
  letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--gold2);margin-bottom:2.5rem;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;
  opacity:0;animation:rise 0.8s 0.2s ease forwards;
}
.hero-overline::before{
  content:'';display:block;width:40px;height:1px;background:var(--gold2);
}
.hero h1{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
  font-size:clamp(3.2rem,8.5vw,7.5rem);
  font-weight:300;line-height:1.05;
  letter-spacing:-0.01em;
  max-width:900px;
  opacity:0;animation:rise 1s 0.4s ease forwards;
}
.hero h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold2)}
.hero h1 strong{font-weight:600}
.hero-body{
  font-size:clamp(1rem,1.8vw,1.2rem);
  font-weight:300;color:rgba(244,239,230,0.6);
  line-height:1.8;max-width:520px;
  margin-top:2.5rem;margin-bottom:3rem;
  opacity:0;animation:rise 0.8s 0.7s ease forwards;
}
.hero-actions{
  display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;
  opacity:0;animation:rise 0.8s 0.9s ease forwards;
}
.btn-gold{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:500;
  letter-spacing:0.04em;background:var(--gold2);color:var(--ink);
  border:none;padding:14px 36px;border-radius:1px;cursor:pointer;
  transition:transform 0.2s,box-shadow 0.2s;text-decoration:none;
  display:inline-block;
}
.btn-gold:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(232,184,75,0.3)}
.btn-line{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:500;
  letter-spacing:0.04em;background:transparent;color:var(--paper);
  border:1px solid rgba(244,239,230,0.2);padding:14px 36px;border-radius:1px;
  cursor:pointer;transition:border-color 0.2s;text-decoration:none;
  display:inline-block;
}
.btn-line:hover{border-color:rgba(244,239,230,0.45)}

.hero-scroll{
  position:absolute;bottom:40px;left:6%;
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.12em;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(244,239,230,0.25);
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
  opacity:0;animation:rise 0.8s 1.2s ease forwards;
}
.hero-scroll::after{
  content:'';display:block;width:1px;height:48px;
  background:linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(244,239,230,0.25),transparent);
}

/* ── SECTION COMMON ── */
section{position:relative;z-index:1;padding:120px 6%}
.s-num{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.14em;
  text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);
  margin-bottom:1.2rem;display:block;
}
.s-title{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
  font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,4rem);
  font-weight:300;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-0.01em;
  margin-bottom:1.5rem;
}
.s-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold2)}
.s-body{
  font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:300;
  color:rgba(244,239,230,0.6);line-height:1.8;
  max-width:560px;
}

/* ── DIVIDER ── */
.divider{
  width:100%;height:1px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--border),transparent);
  position:relative;z-index:1;
}

/* ── PROBLEM SECTION ── */
.problem{background:var(--ink)}
.problem-cols{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;
  margin-top:64px;align-items:start;
}
.problem-stat{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
  font-size:clamp(4rem,10vw,9rem);font-weight:300;
  color:var(--gold2);line-height:1;
  opacity:0.15;
}
.problem-text h3{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
  font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.3;
}
.problem-text p{
  font-size:0.95rem;font-weight:300;
  color:rgba(244,239,230,0.55);line-height:1.85;
}

/* ── MISSION ── */
.mission{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#09090f 0%,#0e0b06 100%);
}
.mission-inner{
  max-width:840px;
  border-left:2px solid var(--gold);
  padding-left:48px;
}
.mission-quote{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
  font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3.5vw,2.8rem);
  font-weight:300;font-style:italic;
  line-height:1.5;color:var(--paper);
  margin-bottom:2rem;
}
.mission-quote strong{font-weight:600;font-style:normal;color:var(--gold2)}
.mission-attr{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.78rem;
  letter-spacing:0.08em;color:var(--gold);
}

/* ── SKILLS ── */
.skills-intro{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;
  margin-bottom:80px;align-items:end;
}
.skills-grid{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1px;
  background:var(--border);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
}
.skill-cell{
  background:var(--ink);
  padding:44px 36px;
  transition:background 0.3s;
  cursor:default;
}
.skill-cell:hover{background:#0d0b08}
.skill-cell.featured{
  grid-column:span 2;
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(201,146,42,0.06),rgba(232,184,75,0.03));
  display:flex;gap:48px;align-items:center;
}
.skill-num{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.68rem;
  letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--gold);
  margin-bottom:1.2rem;display:block;
}
.skill-icon{
  font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:1.2rem;display:block;
}
.skill-cell h3{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
  font-size:1.45rem;font-weight:600;
  margin-bottom:0.7rem;line-height:1.2;
}
.skill-cell p{
  font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:300;
  color:rgba(244,239,230,0.5);line-height:1.8;
}
.skill-cell .skill-tag{
  display:inline-block;margin-top:1rem;
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;
  letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--gold);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(201,146,42,0.3);
  padding-bottom:2px;
}
.featured-num{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
  font-size:clamp(5rem,12vw,10rem);
  font-weight:300;color:var(--gold2);opacity:0.12;
  line-height:1;flex-shrink:0;
}

/* ── METHOD ── */
.method{background:#060609}
.method-steps{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
  gap:48px;margin-top:72px;
}
.method-step{position:relative;padding-top:32px}
.method-step::before{
  content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;
  width:100%;height:1px;background:var(--border);
  transition:background 0.3s;
}
.method-step:hover::before{background:var(--gold)}
.method-step-n{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;
  letter-spacing:0.1em;color:var(--gold);
  margin-bottom:1.2rem;display:block;
}
.method-step h3{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
  font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:400;
  margin-bottom:0.8rem;line-height:1.25;
}
.method-step p{
  font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:300;
  color:rgba(244,239,230,0.5);line-height:1.8;
}

/* ── STAKES ── */
.stakes{background:var(--ink)}
.stakes-row{
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:80px;margin-top:72px;align-items:center;
}
.stakes-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0}
.stakes-item{
  border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  padding:28px 0;
  display:flex;gap:24px;align-items:flex-start;
  transition:border-color 0.3s;
}
.stakes-item:hover{border-color:var(--gold)}
.stakes-item-n{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;
  color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:0.08em;flex-shrink:0;padding-top:4px;
}
.stakes-item h4{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
  font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:6px;
}
.stakes-item p{
  font-size:0.87rem;font-weight:300;
  color:rgba(244,239,230,0.5);line-height:1.75;
}
.stakes-big{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
  font-size:clamp(1.4rem,2.5vw,2rem);
  font-weight:300;font-style:italic;
  line-height:1.6;color:rgba(244,239,230,0.7);
}
.stakes-big strong{font-weight:600;font-style:normal;color:var(--paper)}

/* ── CTA ── */
.cta-sec{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a0804 0%,#05050c 100%);
  text-align:center;padding:160px 6%;
}
.cta-sec h2{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
  font-size:clamp(2.4rem,7vw,6rem);
  font-weight:300;line-height:1.1;
  letter-spacing:-0.01em;
  margin-bottom:1.5rem;
}
.cta-sec h2 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold2)}
.cta-sec p{
  font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:300;
  color:rgba(244,239,230,0.5);line-height:1.8;
  max-width:480px;margin:0 auto 3rem;
}
.cta-form{
  display:flex;gap:0;max-width:440px;margin:0 auto;
}
.cta-input{
  flex:1;padding:14px 20px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  border:1px solid rgba(232,184,75,0.25);
  border-right:none;
  border-radius:1px 0 0 1px;
  color:var(--paper);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;
  font-size:0.92rem;outline:none;
  transition:border-color 0.2s;
}
.cta-input:focus{border-color:rgba(232,184,75,0.6)}
.cta-input::placeholder{color:rgba(244,239,230,0.25)}
.cta-submit{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.8rem;
  letter-spacing:0.04em;background:var(--gold2);color:var(--ink);
  border:none;padding:14px 24px;border-radius:0 1px 1px 0;
  cursor:pointer;font-weight:500;white-space:nowrap;
  transition:background 0.2s;
}
.cta-submit:hover{background:var(--gold-light)}
.cta-note{
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.7rem;
  letter-spacing:0.06em;color:rgba(244,239,230,0.2);
  margin-top:1rem;
}

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer{
  background:var(--ink);border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  padding:40px 6%;display:flex;align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;
}
.foot-logo{
  font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;
  font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:600;color:rgba(244,239,230,0.4);
}
.foot-logo span{color:var(--gold)}
footer p{
  font-size:0.78rem;color:rgba(244,239,230,0.2);
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;letter-spacing:0.04em;
}
.foot-links{display:flex;gap:24px}
.foot-links a{
  font-size:0.78rem;color:rgba(244,239,230,0.2);
  text-decoration:none;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  letter-spacing:0.04em;transition:color 0.2s;
}
.foot-links a:hover{color:rgba(244,239,230,0.5)}

/* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
@keyframes rise{
  from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px)}
  to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}
}
.reveal{
  opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);
  transition:opacity 0.9s ease,transform 0.9s ease;
}
.reveal.visible{opacity:1;transform:none}

/* ── TOAST ── */
.toast{
  position:fixed;bottom:32px;left:50%;
  transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(80px);
  background:var(--gold2);color:var(--ink);
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.82rem;letter-spacing:0.04em;
  padding:12px 28px;border-radius:1px;z-index:999;
  transition:transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175,0.885,0.32,1.275);
  pointer-events:none;white-space:nowrap;
}
.toast.show{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media(max-width:860px){
  .problem-cols,.skills-intro,.stakes-row{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px}
  .skills-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .skill-cell.featured{flex-direction:column;gap:16px}
  .skill-cell.featured{grid-column:span 1}
  .method-steps{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:36px}
  .nav-r a:not(.nav-cta){display:none}
  .cta-form{flex-direction:column}
  .cta-input{border-right:1px solid rgba(232,184,75,0.25);border-bottom:none;border-radius:1px 1px 0 0}
  .cta-submit{border-radius:0 0 1px 1px;padding:14px}
  footer{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:20px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<canvas id="cosmos"></canvas>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="logo">Mind<span>Spark</span></div>
  <div class="nav-r">
    <a href="#mission">Mission</a>
    <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
    <a href="#method">Method</a>
    <a href="#join" class="nav-cta">Join the Mission →</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-overline">Est. 2026 — Building Humanity's Next Chapter</div>
  <h1>The future needs<br><em>better thinkers.</em><br><strong>We build them.</strong></h1>
  <p class="hero-body">MindSpark uses AI to teach children aged 6 and up the foundational skills that drive human civilisation forward — critical thinking, first principles, mathematics, physics, and financial literacy.</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="#join" class="btn-gold">Begin the Mission</a>
    <a href="#skills" class="btn-line">Explore the Curriculum</a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">Scroll to explore</div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- PROBLEM -->
<section class="problem" id="problem">
  <span class="s-num">01 — The Problem</span>
  <h2 class="s-title reveal">Most schools teach children<br><em>what</em> to think.<br>Not <em>how</em>.</h2>
  <p class="s-body reveal">Rote memorisation, standardised tests, and passive learning produce graduates who can recall facts — but struggle to reason through problems they've never seen before. The world doesn't need more fact-storers. It needs thinkers, builders, and solvers.</p>
  <div class="problem-cols">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="problem-stat">72%</div>
      <br>
      <div class="problem-text">
        <h3>of children leave school without the critical thinking skills modern careers demand</h3>
        <p>The gap between what schools teach and what the 21st century actually requires grows wider every year — and AI is accelerating that gap exponentially.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="problem-stat">6</div>
      <br>
      <div class="problem-text">
        <h3>is the age when curiosity and cognitive plasticity are at their most receptive peak</h3>
        <p>The window for building foundational thinking habits is early. MindSpark meets children precisely at this moment — before habits calcify and curiosity dims.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- MISSION -->
<section class="mission" id="mission">
  <span class="s-num">02 — The Mission</span>
  <div class="mission-inner reveal">
    <p class="mission-quote">
      "Every generation inherits the world built by the last. The quality of that world depends entirely on whether the next generation can <strong>reason clearly, think deeply, and act wisely</strong> — in the face of problems we cannot yet imagine."
    </p>
    <div class="mission-attr">— The MindSpark Manifesto</div>
  </div>
  <br><br>
  <p class="s-body reveal">MindSpark exists for one reason: to give every child — regardless of background — access to the cognitive tools that shape civilisation. Through AI-powered adaptive learning, personalised quests, and real intellectual challenge, we plant the seeds of the thinkers humanity urgently needs.</p>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- SKILLS -->
<section id="skills" style="background:var(--ink);padding:120px 6%">
  <div class="skills-intro">
    <div>
      <span class="s-num">03 — The Curriculum</span>
      <h2 class="s-title reveal">Five skills that<br><em>move the world.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <p class="s-body reveal">Not chosen arbitrarily. These are the exact cognitive foundations shared by the scientists, engineers, entrepreneurs, and philosophers who have advanced human civilisation throughout history.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="skills-grid reveal">

    <div class="skill-cell featured">
      <div class="featured-num">01</div>
      <div>
        <span class="skill-icon">🧠</span>
        <h3>Critical Thinking</h3>
        <p>The master skill. The ability to examine claims, identify assumptions, weigh evidence, and arrive at sound conclusions — regardless of the subject. Every other skill on this list is amplified by it. Children who think critically become adults who are nearly impossible to mislead, manipulate, or stall.</p>
        <span class="skill-tag">Foundation of all reasoning</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-cell">
      <span class="skill-num">02</span>
      <span class="skill-icon">⚛️</span>
      <h3>First Principles Thinking</h3>
      <p>Boil any problem down to its fundamental truths and build back up from there. Used by Aristotle, Newton, Tesla, and Elon Musk — it is the engine of genuine innovation and the antidote to assumption-driven thinking.</p>
      <span class="skill-tag">How breakthroughs happen</span>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-cell">
      <span class="skill-num">03</span>
      <span class="skill-icon">∑</span>
      <h3>Mathematics</h3>
      <p>Not arithmetic for its own sake — but mathematics as a language for describing reality. From probability to geometry to calculus, numeracy underpins every field of human endeavour. Children fluent in mathematical thinking see patterns others miss entirely.</p>
      <span class="skill-tag">The language of the universe</span>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-cell">
      <span class="skill-num">04</span>
      <span class="skill-icon">🌌</span>
      <h3>Physics & Science</h3>
      <p>Understanding how the physical world actually works — cause and effect, forces, energy, systems — builds intuition that transcends school. It is the difference between operating within the world and genuinely understanding it.</p>
      <span class="skill-tag">How reality actually works</span>
    </div>

    <div class="skill-cell">
      <span class="skill-num">05</span>
      <span class="skill-icon">💰</span>
      <h3>Financial Literacy</h3>
      <p>Compound interest, risk, value, incentives — the concepts that govern economic life are almost entirely absent from conventional schooling. MindSpark teaches children to understand money as a system, not just a transaction. Financial freedom begins with financial understanding.</p>
      <span class="skill-tag">The skill schools ignore most</span>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- METHOD -->
<section class="method" id="method">
  <span class="s-num">04 — The Method</span>
  <h2 class="s-title reveal">AI that teaches children<br><em>to think,</em> not just to answer.</h2>
  <p class="s-body reveal">MindSpark's AI doesn't give children answers. It asks better questions — guiding each child to arrive at understanding through their own reasoning, at precisely the right level of challenge for their mind.</p>

  <div class="method-steps">
    <div class="method-step reveal">
      <span class="method-step-n">Step 01</span>
      <h3>Adaptive Assessment</h3>
